title: Ep161 Inside Jobs
description: This week, the gals go deep inside a few super sneaky subversive shenanigans. Topics include an all-too-aspirational heist, a mysterious murder suspect gone undetected for decades, and a spot-on pseudonym for the current administration. Pop open a fresh bottle of Rogue Admiral Shiraz, double-check your invoices, and tune in for Inside Jobs. For a full list of show sponsors, visit www.wineandcrimepodcast.com/support
